com.ericsson.jenkins.plugins.dashbeats.model

Class StatsSummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ericsson.jenkins.plugins.dashbeats.model.StatsSummary

  • public class StatsSummary
extends java.lang.Object
    StatsSummary composing of all information to be display on the DashBeats UI. There are 5 widgets on DashBeats UI:
    • Welcome
    • Common Fault Causes
    • Latest Builds
    • Latest Failed Builds
    • Top Failed Jobs
    Created by ekongto on 2014-09-11.
